**Cubits** is a multi-purpose Bitcoin platform. It enables users to buy and sell Bitcoin. Addditionaly, it provides merchant payment system -Cubits Pay.
The service aims to be the quickest way to buy Bitcoin

###Cubits Wallet
Cubits allows users to purchase Bitcoin via bank account. The company provides an option for instant-purchase for those using OKPAY, SOFORT and OBT.
Funds are stored with Cubits Wallet which supports 17 currencies.

###Cubits Pay

Cubits Pay is a service aimed at merchants. 

